<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Server Maintenance</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #666;
        }

        .maintenance-image {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .maintenance-image img {
            width: 50%;
            max-width: 400px;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Server Maintenance</h1>
    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Server Maintenance Image" class="maintenance-image">

    <p>We are currently performing maintenance on our servers. This may cause some temporary disruptions to service. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.</p>

    <p>We expect to have service restored within [estimated maintenance time].</p>

    <p>Thank you for your patience.</p>
</body>
</html>